Package asap.faceengine.faceunit

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FaceUnit
    A facial animation, typically with a peak-like structure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AUFU
    A basic facial animation unit consisting of one AU value.
    FACSFU
    A basic facial animation unit consisting of one FACS configuration The key positions are: start, attackPeak, relax, end.
    KeyframeFaceUnit
    Skeleton implementation for different KeyframeFaceUnits
    KeyframeFacsFU
    MotionUnit for AU keyframe animation
    KeyframeFapsMU
    MotionUnit for MPEG-4 keyframe animation
    KeyframeMorphFU
    Implements a keyframe animation on morphunits e.g.
    MorphFU
    A basic facial animation unit consisting of one morph target.
    MURMLKeyframeMorphFU
    A group of morph targets, controlled by key frames
    PlutchikFU
    A basic facial animation unit consisting of one position on Plutchiks emotion disc (see hmi.faceanimation.converters.EmotionConverter The key positions are: start, attackPeak, relax, end.
    TimedFaceUnit
    When you do not set an end time peg, 'UNKNOWN' is assumed.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FUPlayException
    Thrown whenever a FaceUnit fails during play
